If your congregation's memorial contains any details which vary from those here I would by very grateful if you could send me the details and an image of the memorial. While the list of names submitted by the various congregations for inclusion in the Roll of Honour were correct at the time, in latter years many congregations erected memorials which, in a number of instances, contained the names of those who had been missed originally or they corrected erroneous details.
